"allowSendingOfHats","Enable sending of model files to the server/client?.","allowReceivingOfHats","Enable receiving of model files from the server/client?","serverOptions","These settings affect only the server that loads the mod.","playerHatsMode","Player Hats Mode:\n1 = Free Mode, All players are free to choose what hat to wear.\n2 = Locked mode, all players must wear the same hat, defined in the config.\n3 = Command Giver Mode, what hat you wear is chosen by people who can use commands.\n4 = Hat Hunting Mode, see a mob with a hat, kill it to unlock\n5 = King of the Hat Mode, only one shall wear a hat. The king has to defend their spot or lose the crown!\n6 = Time Active Mode, players unlock more hats the more time they are active on the server.",
"firstJoinMessage","Send a \"First join\" message to the player when they connect to a server for the first time?","lockedHat","What hat do players wear in Locked mode (see playerHatsMode 2).\nIf you want different players to wear different hats, use command giver mode.","startTime","For playerhatsMode 6:\nTime required to be active on the server to unlock the first hat.(In ticks)","timeIncrement","For playerhatsMode 6:\nAmount of extra time required to get the next level hat.\nDefault is 125 (1.25%).\nFor 200% time put 20000",
"randoMobOptions","These settings affect either the client on randoMob settings or Mob Hunting Mode.","clientOnly","These settings affect only the client that loads the mod.","randomMobHat","Do mobs have a random chance of having a hat?\n0 = Disabled (0%)\n100 = All mobs (100%)\n(Client)This follows the randomHat setting, meaning if randomHat is 0, all mobs will wear the favouriteHat setting","renderInFirstPerson","Should your hat render in first person?","enableInServersWithoutMod","Enable hats in servers without the mod?",
"useRandomContributorHats","Allow the use of contributor hats when getting a random hat?\n0 - 100%","shouldOtherPlayersHaveHats","Do other players have hats? Only when enableInServersWithoutMod = 1","resetPlayerHatsOnDeath","Should player hats be reset when they die?\nOnly in unlockable hats modes\n0 = No\n1 = Yes","randomHat","Should each player have a random hat?\nThey randomly change from time to time.\n0 = No\n1 = Yes\n2 = Yes, but not the player!\nOnly when enableInServersWithoutMod = 1","favouriteHat",
